Super class

    Load GUI setup window

    Main method
        "Welcome to HANGMAN, [1] or [2] Players?"
        get player input via mouse click on 1 or 2

        if player chooses 1
          print "which Category would you like"
          list 3 categories
            "animals, places, food" (FILLER)
            get user input via mouse click

            if player inputs choice 1
              create object of choice #1 class
              word list = [words for choice #1]
              call user input method
              call chose random word method (parameters is wordlist)
              call method for counting spaces (parameter is random word)

            if player inputs choice 2
              create object of choice #2 class
              word list = [words for choice #2]
              call chose random word method (parameters is wordlist)
              call method for counting spaces (parameter is random word)
              call user input method

            if player inputs choice 3
              create object of choice #3 class
              Load file with word list
              select random word
              count letters
              create spaces for letter input depending on how much counted letters

         else if player chooses 2
            create object of 2 player class

    Method for getting user input
       print "please fill in the spaces with the word you think it is."
       for up to 6 mistakes (exit once condition is met)
          allow user to enter a letter
          call exception handling method
          if letter is in word
            add letter to correct blank
          else if letter is not in word
            add 1 to mistakes
            call method for graphics (parameter is mistakes)
              
    Method for exception handling
      check to make sure user enters letters (exception handling)

    Method for choosing word (parameter is word_list for given category)
      choose random word form this list
      return random word

    Method for counting spaces(parameter is random word)
      for number of letters in random word
        add one _

    Method for graphics (mistakes)
      add parts of body (pig) as mistakes count goes up
  
Choice #1 class
 
